description.en:
SAFERmoon is an audited static rewards token that also lets you earn additional rewards via staking with no fees while continuing to collect reflection awards (and soon by adding liquidity). 

A 5% transaction fee is redistributed to existing holders, and another 5% transaction fee is used to create a SAFERMOON-BNB pair to generate liquidity on PancakeSwap. Devs have renounced all liquidity, and the contract functions are timelocked.
